openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Simple API
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  "/item":
    patch:
      operationId: updateItem
      summary: Updated item
      responses:
        '204':
          description: Item deleted successfully
components:

    Error:
      type: object
      properties:
        code:
          type: string
        message:
          type: string
      required:
      - code
      - message
